1
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:23,520
Was the door locked when you arrived?

2
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:25,280
It was.

3
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,240
There are no signs of forced entry through the windows either.

4
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:29,320
How many copper keys are there for the shop?

5
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:30,120
And who holds them?

6
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:32,720
Aside from these coffins, my coffin shop...

7
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:34,240
...doesn't have anything valuable.

8
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,880
So I gave a copper key to the pallbearer.

9
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:40,280
It was just to make it convenient for the client to pick up the coffin.

10
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:42,000
The deceased in this coffin...

11
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,240
Do you recognize her?

12
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,480
I do, I do.

13
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:48,360
This is the wife of the pallbearer Wu Tu'an.

14
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,680
Her name is Xiao Lian.

15
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:51,880
We know Wu Tu'an very well.

16
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,920
So he has a copper key in his hand.

17
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,040
The blood spatter pattern...

18
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,240
suggests that while she was still alive,

19
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,720
she was nailed to death inside the coffin.

20
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,600
This must be the crime scene.

21
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:13,720
Guiyi.

22
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:14,720
Investigate closely.

23
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:15,280
Yes.

24
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:20,640
I'll be right back.

25
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,880
Come and take a look!

26
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,800
Take a look!

27
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,040
My Lord!

28
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:50,280
Xiao Lian's death has nothing to do with me!

29
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,800
It has nothing to do with me, My Lord!

30
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,720
If it has nothing to do with you, why did you run?

31
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,960
Why were you acting so sneaky?

32
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,000
Evil spirit.

33
00:02:58,720 --> 00:02:59,800
There's an evil spirit, My Lord!

34
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:02,400
I was afraid of being tainted by the evil spirit.

35
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,240
Evil spirit?

36
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:05,480
Yes.

37
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:07,520
That day, Wu Tu'an and I...

38
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:08,200
Oh.

39
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,560
That is Xiao Lian's husband.

40
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,960
We were carrying a coffin for the client together.

41
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:13,920
But somehow...

42
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,080
...something strange happened.

43
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,160
Coffin in the middle...

44
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,080
Hey!

45
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,480
People on two sides...

46
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,400
Hah!

47
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,800
We lift the coffin...

48
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:26,480
Hey!

49
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:28,640
Steady as Mount Tai...

50
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,520
Hah!

51
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:32,000
The filial son keeps vigil...

52
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,200
Hey!

53
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,240
Departed soul, walk slowly...

54
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:36,000
Hah!

55
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,240
Brother Tu'an.

56
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,440
Why aren't you answering the work chant?

57
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,040
The one in the coffin isn't a dead person.

58
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,080
I saw it.

59
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,320
Inside is a paper effigy.

60
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,120
Pfft, pfft, pfft!

61
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:48,120
You can't say such ominous words while moving the coffin!

62
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,000
It's a paper effigy.

63
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,440
Inside the coffin is a paper effigy.

64
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:53,560
It's ominous.

65
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:53,920
Shh!

66
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:01,400
Client, everything is fine.

67
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,240
Watch your step.

68
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,600
After we finished the work for the Sun family,

69
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,400
and received our reward,

70
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,120
we drank some wine to relax,

71
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,840
and forgot about the matter.

72
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:12,440
But who could have known...

73
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,320
...that very night...

74
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:48,760
Xiao Lian...

75
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:50,840
Darling.

76
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:13,600
Darling.

77
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,080
Darling, what's wrong with you?

78
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,880
Darling, it's me, Xiao Lian. Darling.

79
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:17,840
What's wrong with you?

80
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:32,200
Why don't I find you a job in Chang'an City

81
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:34,000
as a storyteller some other day?

82
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,560
With a mouth like yours,

83
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,160
it's a pity you're a pallbearer.

84
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:38,760
My Lord.

85
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:41,000
I dare not speak a word of falsehood.

86
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:42,520
Although I didn't see it with my own eyes,

87
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:43,840
among us pallbearers,

88
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,160
the word has long since spread.

89
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,760
He must have been possessed by an evil spirit.

90
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,160
My Lord, you may not know,

91
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,560
but what happened afterwards...

92
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,040
...was even weirder.

93
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,320
Darling

94
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,320
Why have you returned so late tonight?

95
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,040
Darling

96
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:32,480
What is that burning in the courtyard?

97
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:38,440
Xiao Lian

98
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,440
Get me something to eat.

99
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:46,680
Sit down first, Darling.

100
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,760
I saved some food for you.

101
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:48,480
I'll go get it.

102
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:04,600
Xiao Lian

103
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:06,360
Xiao Lian

104
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,160
Darling

105
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,440
What is the meaning of this?

106
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:42,000
Darling

107
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,000
Why have you returned so late tonight?

108
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,240
I saved some food for you.

109
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,360
Hurry, sit down and eat.

110
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:56,080
Ah

111
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:56,640
Darling
